    <h1 class="header"> <span class="itemprop" itemprop="name">Chris Marker</span> 
        
        
        
            
            
                <span>(1921&ndash;2012)</span>
    </h1>
    
        <div class="infobar" id="name-job-categories">
            
            
<a href="#director"
onclick="nameJobCategoriesClickHandler(this)" > <span class="itemprop" itemprop="jobTitle">
Director</span></a>                 <span class="ghost">|</span> 
            
            
<a href="#writer"
onclick="nameJobCategoriesClickHandler(this)" > <span class="itemprop" itemprop="jobTitle">
Writer</span></a>                 <span class="ghost">|</span> 
            
            
<a href="#editor"
onclick="nameJobCategoriesClickHandler(this)" > <span class="itemprop" itemprop="jobTitle">
Editor</span></a>            
        </div>
    
        </div>
        </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        
<div class="txt-block" id="name-bio-text">
        <div class="name-trivia-bio-text">
                      <div class="inline" itemprop="description">
Chris Marker was born on July 29, 1921 in Neuilly-sur-Seine, Hauts-de-Seine, France as Christian François Bouche-Villeneuve. He was a director and writer, known for <a href="/title/tt0114746?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk1">Twelve Monkeys</a> (1995), <a href="/title/tt0056119?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk2">La jet&eacute;e</a> (1962) and <a href="/title/tt0084628?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk3">Sans soleil</a> (1983). He died on July 29, 2012 in Paris, France.            <span class="see-more inline nobr-only">
                    <a href="/name/nm0003408/bio?ref_=nm_ov_bio_sm"
>See full bio</a> &raquo;
            </span>
</div>        </div>
</div>

                        
    <div id="name-born-info" class="txt-block">
        <h4 class="inline">Born:</h4> 
<a href="/name/nm0003408/bio?ref_=nm_ov_bth_nm"
> Christian François Bouche-Villeneuve
</a>            <br />
   
  <time datetime="1921-7-29" itemprop="birthDate">
<a href="/search/name?birth_monthday=7-29&refine=birth_monthday&ref_=nm_ov_bth_monthday"
>July 29</a>, 
     
<a href="/search/name?birth_year=1921&ref_=nm_ov_bth_year"
>1921</a>    
  </time>
            in
            <a href="/search/name?birth_place=Neuilly-sur-Seine,+Hauts-de-Seine,+France&ref_=nm_ov_bth_place"
>Neuilly-sur-Seine, Hauts-de-Seine, France</a>
    </div>

<div id="name-death-info" class="txt-block">
    <h4 class="inline">Died:</h4> 
   
  <time datetime="2012-7-29" itemprop="deathDate">
<a href="/search/name?death_monthday=7-29&refine=death_monthday&ref_=nm_ov_dth_monthday"
>July 29</a>, 
     
<a href="/search/name?death_date=2012&ref_=nm_ov_dth_year"
>2012</a>    
  </time>
         (age 91) 
         in <a href="/search/name?death_place=Paris,+France&ref_=nm_ov_dth_place"
