    <h2>Did You Know?</h2>
        <div id="dyk-trivia" class="see-more inline canwrap">
                <h4 class="inline">Trivia:</h4>
An infamously private person, he has never granted an interview and fastidiously keeps his personal life and biographical information hidden. Many believe he sometimes attends events showing his films in disguise.                    <span class="see-more inline">
                        <a href="/name/nm0003408/bio?ref_=nm_dyk_trv_sm#trivia"
